[SN]TITLE[SN]
Warning after metal traps found on Caerphilly mountain

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Police are warning walkers, cyclists and horse riders to be on alert after finding metal traps placed on tracks on Caerphilly mountain.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Officers tweeted photographs of the traps, which appear to be blocks of wood with nails sticking out of them.
There have been previous incidents of paths being blocked.
Gwent Police are appealing for information about the latest incident.
